# EstateTrack — Environment Variables Guide

This template shows all required environment variables for the application.

## 💻 LOCAL DEVELOPMENT (.env.local)
Copy this file to `.env.local` to run the app on your machine.
Do NOT commit `.env.local` to version control.

```env
# 1. Supabase (Get from Project Settings -> API)
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://[PROJECT_REF].supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=[YOUR_ANON_KEY]
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=[YOUR_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY]

# 2. App URL (Localhost for dev)
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000
NODE_ENV=development

# 3. Master Admin Bootstrap
PLATFORM_OWNER_EMAIL=jxilfanx@gmail.com
# Set a strong random string (e.g., openssl rand -hex 32)
BOOTSTRAP_SECRET=your_secure_secret_here

# 4. Push Notifications (VAPID)
# Generate ONCE with: npx web-push generate-vapid-keys
NEXT_PUBLIC_VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY=
VAPID_PRIVATE_KEY=

# 5. Resend (Email)
RESEND_API_KEY=

# 6. Sentry (Error Tracking)
SENTRY_DSN=

# 7. CRON Jobs
# Secret key to authenticate Vercel Cron requests
CRON_SECRET=your_secure_cron_secret

# 8. WhatsApp API (Optional)
WHATSAPP_TOKEN=
WHATSAPP_PHONE_NUMBER_ID=
WHATSAPP_VERIFY_TOKEN=estatetrack_whatsapp_verify_2026

# 9. M-Pesa Daraja API
MPESA_CONSUMER_KEY=        # From Daraja portal → Your App → Details
MPESA_CONSUMER_SECRET=     # From Daraja portal → Your App → Details
MPESA_SHORTCODE=           # Your Paybill or Till number (e.g., 174379 in sandbox)
MPESA_PASSKEY=             # Provided by Safaricom after going live (sandbox has a fixed test passkey)
```

---

## 🚀 PRODUCTION (Vercel Environment Variables)
When deploying to Vercel, enter these EXACT keys in the Vercel Dashboard (Settings -> Environment Variables).

```env
# 1. Supabase (Same as local, but ensure these are Production keys if you use 2 projects)
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://[PROJECT_REF].supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=[YOUR_ANON_KEY]
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=[YOUR_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY]

# 2. App URL (CRITICAL: Must be your actual live domain)
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://www.estatetrack.app
NODE_ENV=production

# 3. Master Admin Bootstrap
PLATFORM_OWNER_EMAIL=jxilfanx@gmail.com
BOOTSTRAP_SECRET=your_secure_secret_here

# 4. Push Notifications (MUST MATCH LOCAL EXACTLY so users don't lose subscriptions)
NEXT_PUBLIC_VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY=
VAPID_PRIVATE_KEY=

# 5. Resend
RESEND_API_KEY=

# 6. Sentry
SENTRY_DSN=

# 7. CRON Jobs
CRON_SECRET=your_secure_cron_secret

# 8. WhatsApp API
WHATSAPP_TOKEN=
WHATSAPP_PHONE_NUMBER_ID=
WHATSAPP_VERIFY_TOKEN=estatetrack_whatsapp_verify_2026

# 9. M-Pesa Daraja API
MPESA_CONSUMER_KEY=        # From Daraja portal → Your App → Details
MPESA_CONSUMER_SECRET=     # From Daraja portal → Your App → Details
MPESA_SHORTCODE=           # Your Paybill or Till number
MPESA_PASSKEY=             # Provided by Safaricom after going live
```
